{"tid":1605263,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香城online 五行破狗聖物","createTime":"2019-09-30T08:38:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T19:08:30.000Z","uid":39858,"like":211,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"a92dea0dc96d12a9978282d8427a381c3ed9f270","tid":1605263,"uid":39858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:38:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XN82emO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXN82emO.jpg&h=0efb37c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aqqLWz9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaqqLWz9.jpg&h=e474a519&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n得知火魔師 施放魔法都係為後排既人走甩 但看到效果不佳 經過多日既思考 <br />\n用火魔法風險實在太高，而且玄學上火生土 對中共有利，而且一比狗搜到好麻煩，而且高風險低回報，魔法的維持時間太短，而且好易傷到自己友。<br />\n<br />\n所以經我多日思考下發現，五行屬水的聖物非二手偈油莫屬<br />\n<br />\n二手偈油 深黑色液體 五行上已經是屬水<br />\n而且可以通街車房都有供應 成本極低<br />\n施法有效時間極極極長 一定冼到仆晒街 而且一定要用化學泡沫或沙先可以清除<br />\n<br />\n如果掉中面罩盾牌會造成短暫石化，所有攻擊性武器都揸唔到<br />\n<br />\n如果在偈油上加木板 可做成滑板效應<br />\n<br />\n所以大家識做啦 以上只係遊戲內容 真實世界切勿模仿"},{"pid":"ff888fcdb2b5dd50752e3a14012aa6b0590d934f","tid":1605263,"uid":39858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:39:28.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"c21392d04b2d7d70303f30eaccc1fe35c8d03dd3","tid":1605263,"uid":39858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:39:39.000Z","msg":"自推 2/10"},{"pid":"87aab7172f4d04ac2a9134abc408399ec6b41b2a","tid":1605263,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:39:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a8d0a696d0b8dfb045f21f99d6b90dd5cb7fb57","tid":1605263,"uid":39858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:39:59.000Z","msg":"自推 3/10"},{"pid":"6c24698a901642ed35355f1196b3d212e1af40fb","tid":1605263,"uid":39858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:40:15.000Z","msg":"自推 4/10"},{"pid":"10ac0bd78ca625e60c84dbb7c68ef1843b2dc637","tid":1605263,"uid"